PRIME RIB RUB

Ingredients
-----------
- 2 Tblsp Kosher Salt
- 2 Tblsp Regular Salt
- 4 Tblsp Black Pepper, ground
- 2 Tblsp Garlic Powder
- 1 Tblsp Thyme, ground
- 1 Tblsp Rosemary, ground


Method
------
0. Mix all ingredients into bowl.
1. Open rib roast in original paper.
2. Rub the mix into the meat, coating all side.
3. Re-wrap the roast.
4. Put into fridge overnight.
5. Next day, roast at 325 for three hours, or 350 for two hours.
